# ── Real family data — must never be committed ────────────────────────────
# The likeliest way this happens: you test the deployed app, hit "Download my
# tree", and the file lands in this folder. Anyone who clones the repo would
# then get those people's names, birthdates and locations.
*-PRIVATE.json
kinship-*.json
*.tree.json

